</owl:ObjectProperty>

<owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#isFallbackRuleOf">
  <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Inverse of hasFallbackRule. Indicates that a rule is the fallback for another rule.</rdfs:comment>
  <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">is fallback rule of</rdfs:label>
  <vaem:rationale>[Pitfall Resolution Agent] Created inverse property for hasFallbackRule: OOPS pitfall: Relationship does not have an inverse relationship defined within the ontology.</vaem:rationale>
