</owl:ObjectProperty>

<owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#isConsequenceDutyOf">
  <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Inverse of hasConsequenceDuty. Indicates that a duty is a consequence of another duty.</rdfs:comment>
  <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">is consequence duty of</rdfs:label>
  <vaem:rationale>[Pitfall Resolution Agent] Created inverse property for hasConsequenceDuty: OOPS pitfall: Relationship does not have an inverse relationship defined within the ontology.</vaem:rationale>
