</owl:ObjectProperty>

<owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://www.semanticweb.org/myontology#resolvesConflictsFor">
  <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Inverse of hasConflictResolutionStrategy. Indicates that a strategy resolves conflicts for a specific policy.</rdfs:comment>
  <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">resolves conflicts for</rdfs:label>
  <vaem:rationale>[Pitfall Resolution Agent] Created inverse property for hasConflictResolutionStrategy: OOPS pitfall: Relationship does not have an inverse relationship defined within the ontology.</vaem:rationale>
